'''The Hooded Gunman''' is a [[massively multiplayer online role-playing game]] created by entrepreneur Warren Dowey.  The game is based on [[The Troubles]] of [[Northern Ireland]]. The game allows the user to build a [[Ulster loyalism|Loyalist]] or [[Irish republicanism|Republican]] criminal gang to build an empire based on [[racketeering]] drugs and killing members of the opposition.  The game has caused controversy in Northern Ireland due to its sensitive nature.

